---
import SectionHead from './SectionHead.astro';
import Tick from './Tick.astro';
---
<section class="about sec wrap" id="about">
  <div class="about__grid">
    <div>
      <SectionHead eyebrow="Who We Are" title="A licensed Adelaide plumbing firm, run by people who live here." />
      <p class="about__lead reveal" style="--rd:60ms">
        Plumber Happy Valley is a fully licensed local business, not a call-centre franchise.
        When you ring us, you reach the people doing the work. We've spent more than ten years
        on homes across the southern suburbs, so we know the older pipework, the hard-water
        wear, and the quirks that come with this part of Adelaide.
      </p>
      <p class="about__body reveal" style="--rd:120ms">
        Every job is quoted upfront and backed by a lifetime labour warranty. We keep our
        vans stocked, our pricing fixed, and our promises simple. If we say 2pm, we're there
        by 2pm.
      </p>
    </div>
    <div class="about__photo reveal" style="--rd:120ms">
      <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1621905252507-b35492cc74b4?w=800&q=80&fit=crop&crop=faces,center" alt="A licensed Plumber Happy Valley technician working on a residential installation" loading="lazy" />
    </div>
    <ul class="about__points reveal" style="--rd:160ms">
      <li><Tick size={14} /><div><strong>Local, not national.</strong> Owned and run in the southern suburbs.</div></li>
      <li><Tick size={14} /><div><strong>One team, start to finish.</strong> The plumber who quotes is the one who fixes it.</div></li>
      <li><Tick size={14} /><div><strong>Compliant work, every time.</strong> Lic. #333997, fully insured.</div></li>
      <li><Tick size={14} /><div><strong>Clean finish.</strong> We leave the site the way we found it.</div></li>
    </ul>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .about__grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1.6fr 1fr 0.9fr; gap: clamp(32px,5vw,68px); align-items: start; }
  .about__photo { overflow: hidden; border-radius: var(--radius); height: 100%; }
  .about__photo img {
    width: 100%; height: 100%; min-height: 280px; object-fit: cover; object-position: center;
    border-radius: var(--radius); display: block; transition: filter .3s;
  }
  .about__photo img:hover { filter: brightness(1.05); }
  .about__lead { font-family: var(--font-body); font-size: clamp(16px,1.4vw,18px); line-height: 1.7; color: var(--color-brand-text); margin: 0 0 18px; }
  .about__body { font-family: var(--font-body); font-size: 15.5px; line-height: 1.7; color: var(--color-brand-muted); margin: 0; }
  .about__points {
    list-style: none; margin: 0; padding: 26px; background: var(--color-brand-surface);
    border: 1px solid rgba(15,23,42,.06); border-radius: var(--radius); display: grid; gap: 16px;
  }
  .about__points li { display: flex; gap: 12px; align-items: flex-start; }
  .about__points li > svg { margin-top: 4px; }
  .about__points div { font-family: var(--font-body); font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.5; color: var(--color-brand-muted); }
  .about__points strong { color: var(--color-brand-secondary); font-weight: 600; }
  @media (max-width: 1024px) { .about__grid { grid-template-columns: 1.4fr 1fr; } .about__photo { grid-column: 1 / -1; } .about__photo img { min-height: 240px; } }
  @media (max-width: 860px) { .about__grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; } }
</style>
